These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, german
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: swimming, biathlon
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, tram
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
2. the german is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | german    | russian |
| Sport         | biathlon | swimming    |
| Transport     | trike     | tram      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate
There are 2 different nationalities: indonesian, australian
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, bike
1. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
2. the indonesian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate  | cola   |
| Nationality   | australian | indonesian  |
| Transport     | bike   | boat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: cooking, camping
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: time-travel, animation
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, climbing
1. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Hobby         | cooking   | camping  |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | time-travel  |
| Sport         | golf   | climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
