.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: artichoke, spinach
The people have 2 different jobs:  nurse, teacher
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, surfing
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the nurse##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
3. the person eating artichoke is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | spinach | artichoke     |
| Job     | teacher | nurse |
| Sport   | surfing | handball    |

 #################################

 
