.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-14::.
There 2 different types of food: lemon, mango
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, skydiving
2 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish
1. the owner of the goldfish is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |
| Food    | mango | lemon  |
| Hobby   | skydiving | puzzles |
| Pet     | cat  | goldfish     |

