.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, board-games
There are 2 different nationalities: spanish, egyptian
2 different pets are kept: horse, ferret
1. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
2. the spanish is on the left of the egyptian##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | board-games | photography |
| Nationality   | spanish     | egyptian     |
| Pet           | ferret          | horse     |

