.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-20::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, martial-arts
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, rock
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, tram
1. the person watching epic movies is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of rock is on the right of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | martial-arts |
| Music-Genre   | folk  | rock  |
| Transport     | tram | airplane    |

 